5. Execute Pipeline problems
----------------------------
Execute Pipeline Activity allows a parent pipeline to call a child pipeline

Master Pipeline
    ↓
Execute Ingestion Pipeline
    ↓
Execute Transformation Pipeline
    ↓
Execute Synapse Load Pipeline

In our project, the transformation pipeline started before the broadband-order ingestion pipeline completed.
This happened because the Execute Pipeline Activity had:Wait on completion = False

How we identified it
We checked:
Parent pipeline run
Child pipeline run
Start and end times
Execute Pipeline Activity settings
Wait on completion setting
Ingestion audit status

We noticed that transformation started while ingestion was still In Progress.
How we overcame it
We:
Stopped the transformation run.
Allowed ingestion to finish.
Validated the raw-layer row count.
Reran transformation for the same BatchId.
Changed Wait on completion to True.
Connected transformation through an Upon Success dependency.

we also added this
Is ingestion status = Succeeded?
        ↓
Yes → Continue
No  → Fail or wait
