6.Dependency-condition problems
-------------------------------
ADF uses dependency conditions to decide when the next activity should run.
The main conditions are:
Upon Success
Upon Failure
Upon Completion
Upon Skip

In our project, the Databricks transformation activity started even though the Oracle Copy Activity had failed.
How we identified it
In ADF Monitor:
Copy Activity status was Failed.
Transformation Activity status was In Progress or Failed.
We inspected the pipeline canvas.
The dependency was configured as Upon Completion.
SOLUTION:
Copy Broadband Orders
        ↓ Upon Success
Transformation
